 href=\"/index.php/House_Waynwood\" title=\"House Waynwood\">Waynwood</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Knightly Houses</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hardyng\" title=\"House Hardyng\">Hardyng</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower\" title=\"House Shett of Gull Tower\">Shett of Gull Tower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Shett of Gulltown\">Shett of Gulltown</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Templeton\" title=\"House Templeton\">Templeton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Waxley\" title=\"House Waxley\">Waxley</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Woodhull\" title=\"House Woodhull\">Woodhull</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Other Houses<br /><small>(noble rank unknown)</small></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Arryn of Gulltown\">Arryn of Gulltown</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Breakstone\" title=\"House Breakstone\">Breakstone</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Crayne\" title=\"House Crayne\">Crayne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Donniger\" title=\"House Donniger\">Donniger</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dutton\" title=\"House Dutton\">Dutton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Egen\" title=\"House Egen\">Egen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hersy\" title=\"House Hersy\">Hersy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lipps\" title=\"House Lipps\">Lipps</a></li>\n<li><a